quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  38,43,"Men jaabinani mo toraare. Men huncani mo lorra makko kan, Men ye…ói mo …ìeynguure makko nden, Men …ìeydani mo ge…óal…ìe e taaniraa…ìe yeru ma…ì…ìe, yurmeende immorde e Amen, e njo…ìdi mu√±al makko ngal, e fii no joomiraa…ìe haqqille hisu…óe …ìen, waajitora, wonnde mu√±al, adday hoyeende e warjeede."
  38,44,"Nde Annabi Ayyuuba tikkannoo debbo makko on, o woondiri piyugol mo loyru teemedere. Men wi'ani mo ontuma : Ko an Ayyuuba, nanngiri sookewo maa ngon, tamannde hu…óo, piyiraa mo …óum, no hunniraa woodoore maa nden, hara a firtaa nden. O wa…ói …óum. Men tawu mo, ko o mu√±√±ii…óo e ko Men jarribori mo kon. O mo∆¥∆¥ii jeyaa…óo. Pellet, ko o …óuu…óunoo…óo tuubugol ruttoo ka Allah."
  38,45,"Janto kadi, an Nulaa…óo, jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen …ìe Men su…ìii, e Nulaa…ìe Amen, …ìe Men immini: Ibraahiima, e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. ∆Åe laatino joomiraa…ìe cemmbe ka …óoftagol Allah, …óa…ì…ìa welayee Makko. ∆Åe woni kadi joomiraa…ìe gii…óe, ja…ìoo…ìe goonga."
  38,46,"Men heertinanii heertinannde, nden woni wuurnugol …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, anntidugol fii galle laakara …óen, hebilarona…óe, golle mo∆¥∆¥e, nodda yim…ìe …ìen e mum."
  38,47,"Kadi, …ìee ka Amen, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìiraa…ìe …óoftagol dewgol Men, su…ìiraa…ìe tammbitagol Nulal Amen ngal, yottina e yim…ìe …ìen."
  38,48,"Janto kadi, an Annabiijo, Ismaa'iila ge…óal Ibraahiima, e Ysa'u, e Zal-Kifli, mantiraa…ìe mantoore labaande, tawde hi…ìe hanndi e mun. Kala e ma…ì…ìe, ko jeyaa…ìe e su…ìaa…ìe mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen ka Allah."
  38,49,"∆äum ko annditirgol …ìee, mantoore labaande, ka Alqur'aana. Ko pellet, hino woodani hulir…ìe Allah …ìen …óoftagol Mo wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde, ka galle laakara."
  38,50,"Nden ruttorde mo∆¥∆¥unde, ko Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …ói …ìe naatoyta √ëalnde Darngal, hara dame majji no udditiranaa…ìe, sa…ónugol …ìe."
  38,51,"Hara ko …ìe so…ì…ìindii…ìe e hoore dan…óe cu…óinanaa…óe …ìe, hi…ìe nodda golloo…ìe ton …ìen, lamndoo…ìe muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói serti, e noone kala e njaram, mo …ìe yi…ói, wano sanngara ekw."
  38,52,"Hino woodani …ìe ton: rew…ìe ra…ì…ìinay…ìe ndaar…óe mun e wor…ìe mun tun, fot…ìe e duu…ìi."
  38,53,"Ko …óum woni ko foda…óon e njo…ìdi laa…ìundi, onon gom…óu…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal. Fii golle mon mo∆¥∆¥e …óen aduna."
  38,54,"Pellet, njo…ìdi jantaandi fii mun ndin …óoo, ko arsike Amen, mo Men arsikoyta gom…óu…ìe …ìen, √ëalnde Darngal. Arsike duumotoo…óo, mo ta∆¥ondirtaa, o lannataa."
  38,55,"Ko jantoo kon, ko njo…ìdi gom…óu…ìe …ìen. Pellet, hino woodani kadi yawtir…ìe keeri Allah …óin geddi e keeferaaku, njo…ìdi sertundi; kam…ìe on, ko ruttorde …ìurnde bonnde woodani …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  38,56,"Njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko Jahannama, huu…ìitaynge …ìe, nge tampina …ìe nguleeki e ooyeende. Hi…ìe mari ton nda…ó…óu…óe, kono …óe bonii da…ó…óu…óe!"
  38,57,"∆äen lepte, ko ndiyam ha…ótu…óam e fatugol, e mbor- di ilatndi e …ìalli yim…ìe leptetee…ìe …ìen ka Yiite. Yo …ìe sulko …óam, sabu ko njaram ma…ì…ìe …óam ittataa …óonka …óan non!"
  38,58,"Hino woodani …ìe lepte goo, nanndu…óe e majje. ∆äen ko nooneeji, …ói …ìe leptiroytee ka laakara."
  38,59,"Si yim…ìe Yiite …ìen naatoyii e magge, …ìe ukkondi- royii hakkunde ma…ì…ìe e weljugol hoynindira, kala e ma…ì…ìe wona e da…óndinagol e oya. Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe wi'i: E hino fedde naatidoyay nde e mon ka Yiite. ∆Åe jaaboo …ìe: Toolii alanaa …ìe, tawde ko …ìe mee…óiray…ìe Yiite ngen, no men mee…óirta nge."
  38,60,"Fedde jokkunoo…ìe …ìeya …ìen wi'ana koohoo…ìe …ìen: ko onon …ìee koohoo…ìe kan, woni toolii alanaa, ko onon defi men …óee lepte muusu…óe, sabu ko mojjinir…óon men kon, bewin…óon men. Ndee √±ii…ìirde Jahannama …óoo, nde bonii √±ii…ìirde naatoo…ìe nge fow."
  38,61,"∆Åe wi'a kadi: Joomi amen, defu…óo men majjugol on, …ìaawo nde peewal ngal ari e amen, sowan mo lepte …óen ka Yiite."